     </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class="u-clearfix u-section-4" id="sec-be0a">\n      <div class="u-clearfix u-sheet u-sheet-1">\n        <div class="u-clearfix u-expanded-width u-layout-wrap u-layout-wrap-1">\n          <div class="u-layout" style="">\n            <div class="u-layout-row" style="">\n              <div class="u-align-center u-container-style u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-layout-cell-1">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-container-layout-1">\n                  <h2 class="u-text u-text-1">TERCER DISTRITO NAVAL "MADERA"</h2>\n                  <p class="u-text u-text-2">Creado el 1 de abril de 1968,‚Äã tiene su base en la ciudad de&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guayaramer%C3%ADn" title="Guayaramer√≠n" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-1">Guayaramer√≠n</a>, y tiene a su cargo un batall√≥n de infanter√≠a de marina, tres bases navales, once capitan√≠as de puerto, y dos puestos de producci√≥n.<br>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class="u-container-style u-image u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-image-1">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-valign-top u-container-layout-2"></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class="u-clearfix u-section-5" id="sec-45de">\n      <div class="u-clearfix u-sheet u-valign-middle u-sheet-1">\n        <div class="u-clearfix u-expanded-width u-gutter-0 u-layout-wrap u-layout-wrap-1">\n          <div class="u-layout" style="">\n            <div class="u-layout-row" style="">\n              <div class="u-align-center u-container-style u-layout-cell u-left-cell u-shape-rectangle u-size-30 u-size-xs-60 u-white u-layout-cell-1" src="">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-container-layout-1">\n                  <h2 class="u-text u-text-1">CUARTO DISTRITO NAVAL "TITICACA"</h2>\n                  <p class="u-text u-text-2">Con base en&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/San_Pedro_de_Tiquina" title="San Pedro de Tiquina" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-1">San Pedro de Tiquina</a>&nbsp;(<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Provincia_de_Manco_Kapac" title="" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-2">provincia de Manco Kapac</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Departamento_de_La_Paz_(Bolivia)" title="Departamento de La Paz (Bolivia)" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-3">departamento de La Paz</a>), a orillas del&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lago_Titicaca" class="mw-redirect u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-4" title="Lago Titicaca">lago Titicaca</a>. Creado el 1 de abril de 1968 , su misi√≥n es la vigilancia fluvial y terrestre a efectos de eliminar el tr√°fico de il√≠citos.en l√≠mites internacionales entre&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bolivia" title="Bolivia" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-5">Bolivia</a>&nbsp;y&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Per%C3%BA" title="Per√∫" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-6">Per√∫</a>.<br>\n                    <br> Sus unidades dependientes son dos batallones de infanter√≠a de marina, un batall√≥n policial naval, dos centros de instrucci√≥n, una direcci√≥n, una base naval, una flotilla y dos capitan√≠as de puerto.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class="u-align-center u-container-style u-image u-layout-cell u-right-cell u-size-30 u-size-xs-60 u-image-1" src="" data-image-width="580" data-image-height="330">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-container-layout-2" src=""></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class="u-clearfix u-section-6" id="sec-67e4">\n      <div class="u-clearfix u-sheet u-sheet-1">\n        <div class="u-clearfix u-expanded-width u-layout-wrap u-layout-wrap-1">\n          <div class="u-layout" style="">\n            <div class="u-layout-row" style="">\n              <div class="u-align-center u-container-style u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-white u-layout-cell-1">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-container-layout-1">\n                  <h2 class="u-text u-text-1">QUINTO DISTRITO NAVAL "SANTA CRUZ"</h2>\n                  <p class="u-text u-text-2"> Ubicado&nbsp; en&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Puerto_Quijarro" title="Puerto Quijarro" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-1">Puerto Quijarro</a>. Fue creado el 19 de julio de 1978 como&nbsp;<b>Quinto Distrito Naval ¬´del Plata¬ª</b>, nombre que mantuvo hasta 1998, cuando adopt√≥ la denominaci√≥n actual. Su jurisdicci√≥n embarca al&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Departamento_de_Santa_Cruz_(Bolivia)" title="Departamento de Santa Cruz (Bolivia)" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-2">departamento de Santa Cruz</a>&nbsp;y los r√≠os&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%ADo_Paraguay" title="R√≠o Paraguay" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-3">Paraguay</a>&nbsp;y&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/R%C3%ADo_Paran%C3%A1" title="R√≠o Paran√°" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-4">Paran√°</a>.<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Quinto_Distrito_Naval_Santa_Cruz_de_la_Sierra#cite_note-S%C3%ADntesis_Hist%C3%B3rica-4" class="u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-palette-1-base u-btn-5">4</a> Sus unidades dependientes son un batall√≥n de infanter√≠a de marina, un batall√≥n de polic√≠a militar, una base naval, una flotilla, cuatro capitan√≠as de puerto y una oficina del&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Servicio_Nacional_de_Hidrograf%C3%ADa_(Bolivia)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new u-active-none u-border-none u-btn u-button-link u-button-style u-hover-none u-none u-text-black u-btn-6" title="Servicio Nacional de Hidrograf√≠a (Bolivia) (a√∫n no redactado)">Servicio Nacional de Hidrograf√≠a</a>.<br>\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class="u-container-style u-image u-layout-cell u-size-30 u-image-1">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-valign-top u-container-layout-2"></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <section class="u-clearfix u-section-7" id="sec-cf83">\n      <div class="u-clearfix u-sheet u-valign-middle-xs u-valign-top-lg u-valign-top-md u-valign-top-sm u-valign-top-xl u-sheet-1">\n        <div class="u-clearfix u-expanded-width u-gutter-0 u-layout-wrap u-layout-wrap-1">\n          <div class="u-layout" style="">\n            <div class="u-layout-row" style="">\n              <div class="u-align-center u-container-style u-layout-cell u-left-cell u-size-30 u-size-xs-60 u-white u-layout-cell-1" src="">\n                <div class="u-container-layout u-container-layout-1">\n                  <h2 class="u-text u-text-1">SEXTO DISTRITO NAVAL "TITICACA"</h2>\n                  <p class="u-text u-text-2">&nbsp;Con base en en&nbsp;<a href="https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cobija_(Bolivia)" title="" class="u-active